<h1 class="page-title">Tables & Reference</h1>
  <p class="lead">Essential charts and roll tables for combat, progression, and world mechanics.</p>

  <div class="tab-container">
    <div class="tab-buttons">
      <button class="tab-button active" onclick="switchTab('tables', 'combat', this)">⚔️ Combat & Action</button>
      <button class="tab-button" onclick="switchTab('tables', 'progression', this)">📈 Progression</button>
      <button class="tab-button" onclick="switchTab('tables', 'size', this)">🐉 Size & Hit Dice</button>
      <button class="tab-button" onclick="switchTab('tables', 'world', this)">💰 Economy & Load</button>
    </div>

    <div class="tab-content active" id="tables-combat">
      <h2 class="section-title">Attack Bonus Differential</h2>
      <table class="wiki-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Attacker's Attack Bonus Higher By</th>
            <th>Bonus to Hit</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>1-5</td><td>+1</td></tr>
          <tr><td>6-10</td><td>+2</td></tr>
          <tr><td>11-15</td><td>+3</td></tr>
          <tr><td>16-20</td><td>+4</td></tr>
          <tr><td>21+</td><td>+5</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
<!-- Speed & Initiative (part of Combat tab) -->
  <h2 class="section-title">RW Difference, Speed, & Initiative</h2>
  <table class="wiki-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Difference</th>
        <th>Bonus</th>
        <th>Damage</th>
        <th>Speed</th>
        <th>Initiative</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>1-5</td><td>+1 to +5</td><td>norm</td><td>1</td><td>d6</td></tr>
      <tr><td>6-7</td><td>6</td><td>norm</td><td>2</td><td>d7</td></tr>
      <tr><td>8-11</td><td>7</td><td>norm</td><td>3</td><td>d6+1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>12-16</td><td>8</td><td>norm</td><td>4</td><td>d8</td></tr>
      <tr><td>17-25</td><td>9</td><td>norm</td><td>5</td><td>d7+1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>26-35</td><td>10</td><td>norm</td><td>6</td><td>d8+1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>36-40</td><td>2</td><td>x2</td><td>7</td><td>d10</td></tr>
      <tr><td>41-50</td><td>3</td><td>x2</td><td>8</td><td>d10+1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>51-60</td><td>4</td><td>x2</td><td>9</td><td>d12</td></tr>
      <tr><td>61-70</td><td>5</td><td>x2</td><td>10</td><td>d12+1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>71-80</td><td>6</td><td>x2</td><td>15</td><td>d20+1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>81-90</td><td>7</td><td>x2</td><td>20</td><td>d30+1 (25=d20+d7)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>91-100</td><td>8</td><td>x2</td><td>30</td><td>2d20</td></tr>
      <tr><td>101-150</td><td>9</td><td>x2</td><td>40</td><td>3d20</td></tr>
      <tr><td>151-200</td><td>10</td><td>x2</td><td>50</td><td>3d20+5</td></tr>
      <tr><td>201-300</td><td>11</td><td>x2</td><td>100</td><td>5d30+5</td></tr>
      <tr><td>301-400</td><td>3</td><td>x3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr>
      <tr><td>401-500</td><td>4</td><td>x3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  
  <p class="wiki-note">
    <strong>Extended Progression Rules:</strong><br>
    • <strong>Damage x3:</strong> Bonus increases +1 per 100 Difference (+12 at 1200).<br>
    • <strong>Damage x4:</strong> Resets to +4 at 1301 Difference (+13 at 2201).
  </p>
</div>
